{
  "id": "adv_main_03_10_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章49話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり五人で練習したいと聞いた時は驚いたけど\n今後の方針が決まったようで、良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised when you suddenly said you wanted to practice as a five‚\nbut it sounds like you've all decided on how to move forward‚ which is great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "渚、すず、芽衣、沙季、そして琴乃\n五人で、また月のテンペストとして活動していくんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ Suzu‚ Mei‚ Saki‚ and Kotono.\nYou five will be working together again as Moon Tempest‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。今まで、沢山迷惑をかけてしまって……\n本当にすみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I've caused so much trouble…\nI'm truly sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それと……私が戻ってくることを受け入れてくれて\n本当にありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… for accepting me back‚\nthank you so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、謝るのは今回限りにしよう\nもう気持ちは十分に伝わってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ let's stop with the apologies.\nI understand how you feel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "これで元の……\nいや、パワーアップした新生月ストの誕生だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this‚ the original…\nNo‚ the birth of a powered-up‚ new Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さて、五人に戻ったとなると……\n記者会見を開いた方がいいだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ that you're back to five members…\n…we should hold a press conference.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私も、世間や、ファンの人達に\n向き合う場がほしいと思っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've also been wanting to\nhave a chance to face the public and our fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 60.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……\nその記者会見ですが、私一人で出てもいいでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However…\n…for the press conference‚ can I go alone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私が招いた事態ですから……説明も、謝罪の責任も\n私にあると思います。だから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I caused this situation… I believe the responsibility to explain and apologize\nrests on me. That's why――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、琴乃ちゃん。ストップ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ stop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1687281923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 78.5326736448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "また一人で抱え込もうとして……\nそういうところですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trying to shoulder everything on your own again…\nThat's exactly what's wrong with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7972772599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の悪い癖ですわね\nいい加減、直してくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a bad habit of yours‚ Kotono.\nIt's time to fix it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4639439266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、じゃあ……どうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but then… what should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1517758844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "五人で記者会見に出よう？\n私達、五人で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's go to the press conference as a five.\nThe five of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3639439266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "けど、説明の責任があるのは私なんだし\nみんなまで何か言われたら……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm the one who's responsible for explaining…\n…What if everyone gets dragged into this?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3972772599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "また、月のテンペストとして、五人で進んでいくと\n決めたんです。それも全て、承知の上ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've decided\nto move forward as Moon Tempest‚ as five. And we're doing it knowing all that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3972772599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。私達を、舐めないでくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph. Don't underestimate us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6983972706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。そうね……\nみんな……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You're right…\nEveryone… thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7639439266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "決まりだな\nそれじゃあ、俺の方で準備をしておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's settled then.\nI'll make the arrangements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.0972787858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_evening",
      "startTime": 131.6972772599
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 131.9732656317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ここで練習するのは……凄く久しぶりな気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it’s been a long time since we practiced here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7732656317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "合わせるのも久しぶりだし\nとりあえず最初は、軽く流す程度にしておこっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been a while since we practiced together‚ too‚\nso let's start off with something light.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3306105932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、琴乃。今のあなたの実力がどれほどのものか……\n私達が見定めて差し上げますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Kotono. We'll see how good you are…\n…we'll be the judge of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4306105932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。それじゃあ――始めよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Then let's―― begin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7468257742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 159.1770753222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃、なかなかやりますわね）\n（指先まで、意識を集中しているのが分かる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono‚ you're not bad.）\n（I can tell you're focused on every movement…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0639413835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "（安定感が抜群に増していて）\n（ほんの少しのブレさえ感じません……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her stability has increased dramatically‚）\n（I don't feel even a slight waver…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.4972747168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "（でも――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.2934766929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "（私達だって……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We've grown too…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.0742547035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "（っ……凄い……こうして一緒に合わせると）\n（みんなの成長を、肌で感じる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Amazing… practicing together like this）\n（I can feel everyone's growth… ）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.9279621046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
