      "text": "（私も、みんなみたいに強くなりたい……！）\n（叩き潰すんじゃない。暗闇を払うような、強さを！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I want to become strong like you all…!）\n（Not by crushing others. But with a strength that dispels the darkness!）",
        "id": ""
      },
